  "contents": "\n\n<article>\n  <div class=\"page-actions\">\n    <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular/edit/master/packages/core/src/di/metadata.ts?message=docs(core)%3A%20describe%20your%20change...#L246-L245\" aria-label=\"Suggest Edits\" title=\"Suggest Edits\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">mode_edit</i></a>\n    <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular/tree/6.0.0-beta.7/packages/core/src/di/metadata.ts#L246-L245\" aria-label=\"View Source\" title=\"View Source\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"breadcrumb\">\n    <script type=\"application/ld+json\">\n      {\n        \"@context\": \"http://schema.org\",\n        \"@type\": \"BreadcrumbList\",\n        \"itemListElement\": [\n        ]\n      }\n    </script>\n    \n  </div>\n  <header class=\"api-header\">\n    <h1 id=\"host\">Host<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/Host#host\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n    <label class=\"api-type-label decorator\">decorator</label>\n    \n    \n    <label class=\"api-status-label stable\">stable</label>\n  </header>\n  <aio-toc class=\"embedded\"></aio-toc>\n\n  <div class=\"api-body\">\n    \n  <p class=\"short-description\"></p><p>Host decorator and metadata.</p>\n<p></p>\n  \n  \n  \n  \n\n  \n  \n<section class=\"description\">\n  <h2 id=\"description\">Description<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/Host#description\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <p>For more details, see the <a href=\"guide/dependency-injection\">\"Dependency Injection Guide\"</a>.</p>\n<h3 id=\"example\">Example<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/Host#example\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h3>\n<code-example>\nclass OtherService {}\nclass HostService {}\n\n@<a href=\"api/core/Directive\" class=\"code-anchor\">Directive</a>({selector: 'child-directive'})\nclass ChildDirective {\n  logs: string[] = [];\n\n  constructor(@<a href=\"api/core/Optional\" class=\"code-anchor\">Optional</a>() @<a href=\"api/core/Host\" class=\"code-anchor\">Host</a>() os: OtherService, @<a href=\"api/core/Optional\" class=\"code-anchor\">Optional</a>() @<a href=\"api/core/Host\" class=\"code-anchor\">Host</a>() hs: HostService) {\n    // os is null: true\n    this.logs.push(`os is null: ${os === null}`);\n    // hs is an instance of HostService: true\n    this.logs.push(`hs is an instance of HostService: ${hs instanceof HostService}`);\n  }\n}\n\n@<a href=\"api/core/Component\" class=\"code-anchor\">Component</a>({\n  selector: 'parent-cmp',\n  viewProviders: [HostService],\n  template: '&#x3C;child-directive>&#x3C;/child-directive>',\n})\nclass ParentCmp {\n}\n\n@<a href=\"api/core/Component\" class=\"code-anchor\">Component</a>({\n  selector: 'app',\n  viewProviders: [OtherService],\n  template: '&#x3C;parent-cmp>&#x3C;/parent-cmp>',\n})\nclass App {\n}\n\n</code-example>\n\n</section>\n\n  \n\n\n  \n\n\n  </div>\n</article>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - api/core\n - api/core/HostDecorator\n - guide/aot-compiler\n - guide/dependency-injection-in-action\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - api/core/Component\n - api/core/Directive\n - api/core/Host#description\n - api/core/Host#example\n - api/core/Host#host\n - api/core/Optional\n - guide/dependency-injection\n - https://github.com/angular/angular/edit/master/packages/core/src/di/metadata.ts?message=docs(core)%3A%20describe%20your%20change...#L246-L245\n - https://github.com/angular/angular/tree/6.0.0-beta.7/packages/core/src/di/metadata.ts#L246-L245\n-->"
}